Logfile:
    message from watchdog
    process messages (errors, entry into a relevant area of code)
    <time of day><process name><message><other>
        to write to the logfile, each process must lock, write, flush, release lock

watchdog:
    monitor processes
    read from process file
    send messages to logfile that it is alive

Process File(Global file):
        name of process and its PID
        each process writes its name and PID to this file when it starts
        to write to the process file, each process must lock, write, flush, release locks